title: National Register of Historic Places listings in Erie County, Ohio
text:
This is a list of the National Register of Historic Places listings in Erie County, Ohio.
This is intended to be a complete list of the properties and districts on the <a href="National%20Register%20of%20Historic%20Places">National Register of Historic Places</a> in <a href="Erie%20County%2C%20Ohio">Erie County</a>, <a href="Ohio">Ohio</a>, <a href="United%20States">United States</a>. Latitude and longitude coordinates are provided for many National Register properties and districts; these locations may be seen together in an online map.
There are 179 properties and districts listed on the National Register in the county, including 2 <a href="National%20Historic%20Landmark">National Historic Landmark</a>s. The city of <a href="Sandusky%2C%20Ohio">Sandusky</a> is the location of 114 of these properties and districts; they are <a href="National%20Register%20of%20Historic%20Places%20listings%20in%20Sandusky%2C%20Ohio">listed separately</a>, while the remaining 65 sites, including both National Historic Landmarks, are listed here.
